wydget
======

wydget is a GUI library for pyglet

http://www.pyglet.org/


Disclaimer
----------

THIS SOFTWARE IS IN HEAVY DEVELOPMENT AND THE API WILL CHANGE!

See BUGS for more information.


Requirements
------------

wydget requires pyglet and the "layout" contributed package in the pyglet repository

To run wydget's tests, try::

  PYTHONPATH=../../:../layout run_tests.py [tests/ xml file]

By default it will run all xml files in the tests directory.


Installation
------------

Not yet. See above disclaimer.


